{"tid":252261,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[求評] 6月鹿兒島+霧島+指宿行程","createTime":"2017-05-21T14:33:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-23T01:31:35.000Z","uid":10679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7b9294891f2cce14731a9df56681cc4ed7bbd885","tid":252261,"uid":10679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:33:53.000Z","msg":"巴打，第一次獨遊，影相多，唔揸車，鹿兒島機場KOJ 出入<br />\n<br />\nDay 1<br />\n三點幾四點落機<br />\n應該住中央站附近（未睇）<br />\ncheck in完行下Amu plaza，天文館通，係附近食完野就番酒店<br />\n<br />\nDay 2<br />\n仙嚴園<br />\n石橋紀念公園<br />\n櫻島火山<br />\n水族館<br />\n城山展望台<br />\n<br />\n如果唔夠時間就唔去水族館<br />\n<br />\nDay 3<br />\n高千穗牧場<br />\n霧島神宮<br />\n<br />\nDay 4<br />\n指宿 砂浴，露天溫泉<br />\n<br />\nDay 5<br />\n鹿兒島機場（一點半機）<br />\n<br />\n求評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇咩要注意？<br />\n我上次去大阪用hsbc提款卡係當地atm攞日元，例如機場／7-11咁。鹿兒島多唔多atm？<br />\n<br />\n原本想去宮崎睇復活節島石像同高千穗峽，但係唔夠時間同太遠，都係唔去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dce2c4f3f29d20a1e600623f00c42368d313a0f4","tid":252261,"uid":7108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:37:06.000Z","msg":"Day 3 你唔揸車要預時間搭車<br />\n啲車好疏"},{"pid":"573be520245d7627bed2af2dbe09238a46ebf957","tid":252261,"uid":10679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:45:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Day 3 你唔揸車要預時間搭車<br />\n啲車好疏</blockquote><br />\n你講搭JR去到霧島市之後轉去霧島神宮果d巴士？"},{"pid":"41ab606f3357d14f20a051a37f012238237d4eea","tid":252261,"uid":65931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:46:39.000Z","msg":"Day 2 想點<br />\n識分身？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26747b181a2c7bca448e8266b965e9d5195b8340","tid":252261,"uid":10679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:54:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Day 2 想點<br />\n識分身？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果早d起身去櫻島火山坐巴士tour，完左去仙巖園呢？"},{"pid":"a17d43954594fe99242bde8897677807117748b2","tid":252261,"uid":10679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T15:07:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5215635e0464d4c9d96576e75a9ceaedd5b4d96a","tid":252261,"uid":65931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T15:19:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Day 2 想點<br />\n識分身？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果早d起身去櫻島火山坐巴士tour，完左去仙巖園呢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實視乎你去到當打卡就算定認真行<br />\n櫻島我諗快極都半day<br />\n仙嚴園好大，認真行都半day<br />\n我自己就唔會將呢兩個地方放同一日"},{"pid":"8bca57205649fde2fddf8fcec95d8bffd8577fb8","tid":252261,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T15:22:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Day 2 想點<br />\n識分身？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果早d起身去櫻島火山坐巴士tour，完左去仙巖園呢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實視乎你去到當打卡就算定認真行<br />\n櫻島我諗快極都半day<br />\n仙嚴園好大，認真行都半day<br />\n我自己就唔會將呢兩個地方放同一日</blockquote><br />\n水族館都可3,4個鐘<br />\n城山展望台幾偏辟 行上去的話<br />\n黑到爆<br />\n夜晚無車走行死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b9917d77e7867924342d8fd14bb0afbb74c8c56","tid":252261,"uid":10679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T16:01:33.000Z","msg":"改左少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDay 1<br />\n三點幾四點落機<br />\n應該住中央站附近（未睇）<br />\ncheck in完行下Amu plaza，天文館通，係附近食完野就番酒店<br />\n<br />\nDay 2<br />\n櫻島火山巴士tour<br />\n水族館<br />\n<br />\nDay 3<br />\n城山展望台<br />\n仙巖園<br />\n<br />\nDay 4<br />\n高千穗牧場<br />\n霧島神宮<br />\n大浪池<br />\n<br />\nDay 5<br />\n鹿兒島機場（一點半機）"},{"pid":"33a4cf5d8a16a606538c2630d9dd95bd714ca519","tid":252261,"uid":28599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T16:25:47.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n7月去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" cl